thread.title_full: Lauryn Rose reviewed by Mrs McD. Ireland

author: Mrs McD. Ireland
title: Mrs McD. Ireland
text: I was delighted to have received a gift voucher for a bracelet and chose the Think of me Charm bracelet with the Rose Gold,Silver and Gold charms.The bracelet arrived beautifully packaged on Friday having just been ordered on the Wednesday .It is a beautiful ,small ,delicate and original bracelet with significance for me .A special thank you to Phillip who was extremely helpful and professional .
